	<clause id="_secretariat_of_the_jctlm" obligation="normative"><title>Secretariat of the JCTLM</title><p id="_f452bf9c-4196-4d2c-8195-5db1430b8013">The operation of JCTLM is managed by the JCTLM Secretariat.</p>
	<clause id="_11" obligation="normative">
	
	<p id="_09665968-b156-4ee8-9f08-78ebb88ec8bb">The role of the Secretariat will include: the calling of meetings; preparation of agendas and action lists; and the maintenance of the JCTLM database and website. The procedures for the operation of the Secretariat are available at: <link target="https://www.bipm.org/en/committees/jc/jctlm/jctlm-nominations-and-review.html"/></p>
	</clause>
